Recommended Books for CMPE 202 :  1. Fowler, Martin. UML Distilled: A Brief Guide to the Standard Object Modeling Language.  Addison-Wesley, 2004.  2. Gamma, Erich. Design Patterns: Elements of Reusable Object-oriented Software. Addison-Wesley, 1995.  3. Hundermark, Peter.  Do Better Scrum. 4. Kniberg, H & Skarin M.  Kanban and Scrum.
